# 🧠 4. CORE DESIGN DECISIONS

---

## ✅ Precomputation (IMPORTANT)

Instead of computing live:

👉 Compute in background
👉 Store results

---

## ✅ Lightweight Storage

Store only:

* Aggregated stats
  NOT raw trades

---

## ✅ Filtering Strategy

Filters applied at:

* DB query level

---

